<link href="adcp.css" rel="stylesheet"><entry><xh5>red hot peppers • red hots</xh5><p> <i>red hot peppers</i>—(also: Chili peppers) a pungent red pod of the genus <i>Capsicum:</i> Add the juice of <sup>1</sup>⁄2 lemon, salt and a good pinch of dried <u>red hot peppers</u>.</p><p><i>red hots</i>—(U.S.) 1. a type of small candy with a powerful cinnamon flavor: <u>Red Hots</u> are perhaps the best known type of spicy candy. 2. hotdogs, especially sold by street vendors: Whether you call them hot dogs, <u>red hots</u> or frankfurters, try some new recipe ideas.</p> </entry>
